txt.en: Hungry (and therefore violent) snow-cats can be found in the western hills of the High Knolls.\n\nYou should fend off the hungry beasts who would like nothing better than to eat you up.
The wildcats of the High Knolls have invaded the hillsides where wild goat herds now starve without food, their own dwindling food supply making them especially hostile.
